				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td><p>L'un des types possibles de l'&eacute;l&eacute;ment <span class="literal">input</span>: <span class="literal">button</span> | <span class="literal">checkbox</span> | <span class="literal">file</span> | <span class="literal">hidden</span> | <span class="literal">image</span> | <span class="literal">password</span> | <span class="literal">radio</span> | <span class="literal">reset</span> | <span class="literal">submit</span> | <span class="literal">text</span>.</p>
